COGNUS public-main

This repository snapshot contains original COGNUS code and documentation plus derivative work based on Hyperledger Cello, which is distributed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

The public-main branch intentionally excludes:
- private credentials and bootstrap secrets;
- generated runtime state, cryptographic material, and ledgers;
- copied upstream documentation not authored for this snapshot;
- third-party PDFs and local working files that are not part of the public artifact.

Public attribution and licensing are defined by:
- LICENSE
- CITATION.cff
- ARTIFACT.md
